name: newhorrofantasy_style SD 1.5 Embedding
description:
Hi guys!

Why create an embedding about my succesful model? Because is funny xD. It returns images with a 2010s horror and fantasy style illustration.

If you wanna test it, you can put this word on the prompt: art by newhorrorfantasy_style

This model only works on SD 1.5 .

if you wanna support me, you can buy me a coffee: https://www.buymeacoffee.com/elrivx
